{"type": "game", "name": "BUTCHER", "steam_appid": 474210, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "dlc": [536590, 555420], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/_Butcher__gif1_frame1.gif?t=1741358342\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a heartless killing machine bent on eradicating humans in <i>BUTCHER</i>, a relentless 2D shooter that pushes the boundaries of action and pixelated gore. In a dystopian future where humanity is on the brink of extinction, you become the ultimate killing machine, driven by an insatiable thirst for destruction. As you navigate this grim world, you\u2019ll face bloodthirsty foes in fast-paced, ultra-violent combat that leaves no room for mercy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/_Butcher__gif2_frame1.gif?t=1741358342\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a beautifully crafted pixel art style that pays homage to classic games while delivering a modern twist. The atmospheric soundtrack enhances the tension as you blast through waves of enemies, using an arsenal of brutal weapons designed for maximum carnage. Master your skills with precise controls and a satisfying combat system that rewards quick reflexes and strategic thinking. Each encounter is an opportunity to showcase your prowess as you adapt your approach to survive in this unforgiving environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/_Butcher__gif3_frame1.gif?t=1741358342\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse diverse and challenging levels, each filled with unique environmental obstacles and menacing foes that will test your abilities. As you progress, discover hidden secrets and unlock new weapons, and upgrades to 