42\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse diverse and challenging levels, each filled with unique environmental obstacles and menacing foes that will test your abilities. As you progress, discover hidden secrets and unlock new weapons, and upgrades to customize your killing machine.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/extras/_Butcher__gif4_frame1.gif?t=1741358342\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to embrace the chaos? Step into the world of <i>BUTCHER</i> and show no mercy as you unleash destruction on everything that stands in your way.</p>", "short_description": "BUTCHER is a fast-paced, blood-soaked 2D shooter where carnage is the only way forward. Become a ruthless cyborg tasked with eradicating humanity, leaving nothing but blood, guts, and destruction in your wake. There's no such thing as too much violence in this grim, retro-styled gorefest.", "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong>, French, German, Spanish - Spain, Portuguese - Portugal, Portuguese - Brazil<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "reviews": "\u201cHARDCORE\u201d<br>John Romero<br><br>\u201cI\u2019ve enjoyed many games in 2015, but few have put a smile on my face the way Butcher has.\u201d<br>Kotaku<br><br>\u201cI can think of lots of reasons why shotgunning your way through some 2D pixels might turn your day around, but whatever the cause I recommend Butcher.\u201d<br>Rock, Paper, Shotgun<br>", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/header.jpg?t=1741358342", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1741358342", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474210/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1741358342", "website": "https://butcher.thd.vg", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</str